{"uid":"7f3937284466a481","name":"Verify Admin can change Admin role to User","fullName":"tests.test_cases.tests_ui.test_organization_change_member_roles.TestUIOrganizationChangeMemberRoles#test_admin_change_admin_to_user","historyId":"19afc2b8622c3ec986feaf54241304d6","time":{"start":1771123192054,"stop":1771123393971,"duration":201917},"description":"\n- Login with valid credentials.\n- Create new organization via **API**.\n- Signup `second user`.\n- Invite `second user` to organization with `Admin` role via **API**.\n\n### Verify that:\n\n- `Admin` can change user role from `Admin` to `User`\n- User after changing role from `Admin` to `User`:\n\n- **Cannot** access organization `Settings`.\n- **Cannot** access organization `Billing`.\n","descriptionHtml":"<div style='line-height:1.6;'><ul>\n<li>Login with valid credentials.</li>\n<li>Create new organization via <strong>API</strong>.</li>\n<li>Signup <span style='background-color:#D3D3D3; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px; font-family:monospace;'>second user</span>.</li>\n<li>Invite <span style='background-color:#D3D3D3; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px; font-family:monospace;'>second user</span> to organization with <span style='background-color:#D3D3D3; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px; font-family:monospace;'>Admin</span> role via <strong>API</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Verify that:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><span style='background-color:#D3D3D3; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px; font-family:monospace;'>Admin</span> can change user role from <span style='background-color:#D3D3D3; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px; font-family:monospace;'>Admin</span> to <span style='background-color:#D3D3D3; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px; font-family:monospace;'>User</span></li>\n<li>\n<p>User after changing role from <span style='background-color:#D3D3D3; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px; font-family:monospace;'>Admin</span> to <span style='background-color:#D3D3D3; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px; font-family:monospace;'>User</span>:</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Cannot</strong> access organization <span style='background-color:#D3D3D3; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px; font-family:monospace;'>Settings</span>.</p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Cannot</strong> access organization <span style='background-color:#D3D3D3; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px; font-family:monospace;'>Billing</span>.</li>\n</ul></div>","status":"passed","flaky":false,"newFailed":false,"newBroken":false,"newPassed":true,"retriesCount":0,"retriesStatusChange":false,"beforeStages":[{"name":"test_config","time":{"start":1771123191362,"stop":1771123191365,"duration":3},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"stepsCount":0,"attachmentsCount":0,"hasContent":false,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"_function_scoped_runner","time":{"start":1771123191365,"stop":1771123191365,"duration":0},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"stepsCount":0,"attachmentsCount":0,"hasContent":false,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"page_manager","time":{"start":1771123191365,"stop":1771123192051,"duration":686},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"stepsCount":0,"attachmentsCount":0,"hasContent":false,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"data_manager","time":{"start":1771123192051,"stop":1771123192051,"duration":0},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"stepsCount":0,"attachmentsCount":0,"hasContent":false,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"users_manager","time":{"start":1771123192051,"stop":1771123192052,"duration":1},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"stepsCount":0,"attachmentsCount":0,"hasContent":false,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"apolo_cli","time":{"start":1771123192052,"stop":1771123192052,"duration":0},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldDispla